## 2. Service Description

### 2.1 Core Functionality

roast.dev is a browser extension that facilitates code reviews using Large Language Models (LLMs). The Service:
- Integrates with GitHub and GitLab platforms
- Connects to LLM providers using your API keys
- Provides an interface for AI-powered code reviews
- Is available through Chrome Web Store and Firefox Add-ons platforms

### 2.2 Infrastructure

- Website is hosted on Cloudflare
- Customer accounts and payments are managed through Stripe
- Browser extensions are distributed through official browser stores
- No dedicated servers for code processing

